{"lemma":"مَضْمُونٌ","slug":"مَضْمُونٌ","root":"ض.م.ن","root_slug":"ض-م-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-م-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26053"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B6%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%86%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"content"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"contents of a paper"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the bottom line of a written text"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a thing for which some person is guarantee"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"passive participle of ضَمِنَ (ḍamina); guaranteed","tags":["participle"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"passive participle of ضَمِنَ (ḍamina); insured","tags":["participle"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the passive participle of ضَمِنَ (ḍamina)."},"ipa":["/madˤ.muːn/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26053","headword_ar":"مَضْمُونٌ","root":"Dmn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"pass. part. n. of 1 in the first of the senses assigned to the latter above: you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aYo'N","text_ar":"شَىْءٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDomuwnN","text_ar":"مَضْمُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"such as property, or the payment of a debt, &c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ensured by an acknowledgment of responsibility for it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDomuwnu kitaAbK","text_ar":"مَضْمُونُ كِتَابٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA fiY Dimonihi","text_ar":"مَا فِى ضِمْنِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~ihi","text_ar":"طَيِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The contents of a writing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"letter;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is infolded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"included, in a writing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"letter; what is implied therein;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is indicated therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDaAmiynu","text_ar":"مَضَامِينُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaDaAmiynu","text_ar":"المَضَامِينُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A 'Obeyd, S, Msb, K,) of which the sing. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDomuwnN","text_ar":"مَضْمُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A 'Obeyd, Msb, K,) and one may also say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDomuwnapN","text_ar":"مَضْمُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nasamapN","text_ar":"نَسَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What are"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comprised"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the loins of the stallions;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd, S, Msb, K;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the progeny"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereof, in the elemental state"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:) or, accord. to Aboo-Sa'eed, [though the reverse is generally held to be the case,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmalaAqiyHu","text_ar":"المَلَاقِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies what are in the backs of the he-camels, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaDaAmiynu","text_ar":"المَضَامِينُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what are in the bellies of the females."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lqH","text_ar":"لقح"},{"kind":"text","text":".) The selling of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mDAmyn","text_ar":"مضامين"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mlAqyH","text_ar":"ملاقيح"},{"kind":"text","text":"is forbidden. (S.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDaAmiynu","text_ar":"مَضَامِينُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miDomaAnN","text_ar":"مِضْمَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDomuwnu Alyadi","text_ar":"مَضْمُونُ اليَدِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maxobuwnuhaA","text_ar":"مَخْبُونُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEoluwluhaA","text_ar":"مَعْلُولُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Diseased in the arm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TK;) applied to a man. (TA. [See 1, last sentence, which indicates a more particular meaning.])"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D9%85%D8%B6%D9%85%D9%88%D9%86/","headword_ar":"مضمون الجملة","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_24","lexicon_en":"Al-Tahānawī, Kashshāf Iṣṭilāḥāt al-Funūn wa-l-ʿUlūm (d. 1777 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كشّاف اصطلاحات الفنون والعلوم للتهانوي","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=42882#31be6d","body_html":"<span>مضمون الجملة:</span><br><span>[في الانكليزية] Meaning of a sentence ،content </span><br><span>[ في الفرنسية] Sens d'une phrase ،contenu </span><br><span>عند النحاة قد يراد به مصدر تلك الجملة المضاف إلى الفاعل، أي فيما إذا كان مناط الفائدة نسبة المسند إلى الفاعل. فمضمون قام زيد مثلا قيام زيد. وإلى المفعول أي فيما إذا كان مناط الفائدة النسبة الإيقاعية. فمضمون ضرب زيد على البناء للمفعول ضرب زيد بمعنى مضروبية زيد. والمصدر المقيّد بالحال فيما إذا كان مناط الفائدة الحال نحو أصحب مع زيد مسرورا فإمّا أن تنفعه أو ينفعك، فإنّ مضمون الجملة هنا صحبة زيد وقت السرور فاحفظه فإنّه من المواهب الدقيقة الجليلة، هكذا ذكر المولوي عصام الدين في حاشية الفوائد الضيائية في بحث المفعول المطلق. وقد يراد به ما يفهم من الجملة ولم تكن الجملة موضوعة له كالاعتراف المفهوم من قولنا له عليّ ألف درهم، والحقّ المفهوم من قولنا زيد قائم، كذا ذكر أبو البقاء في حاشية الفوائد الضيائية في هذا المقام.</span>"}]}}